<l>ceviccolluṅ cērnta nakaiyu mavittoḻuka </l>
<l>lāṉṟa periyā rakattu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>While in the presence of the sovereign, ministers should neither whisper to nor smile at others.</l>
